<taxonomicName authority="Cresson" authorityName="Cresson" box="[687,1008,1779,1801]" class="Insecta" family="Ephydridae" genus="Neoephydra" kingdom="Animalia" order="Diptera" pageId="45" pageNumber="46" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="abrupta">
<emphasis box="[687,899,1779,1801]" italics="true" pageId="45" pageNumber="46">Neoephydra abrupta</emphasis>
(Cresson)
</taxonomicName>
. (61) epandrium, cerci, surstyli, posterior view; (62) same, lateral view; (63) surstylus, lateral view.
</paragraph>
